data.text:
I'm having a Customer Quality Audit very soon and I've got a question. Maybe someone can help me out. Below is the question. I'm assuming this is in regards to a special charateristic called out on a print. I would like to know the definition of Delta C and Delta S.

Are Delta "C" / Delta "S" conditions controlled?

Thank you
